<html>
<head>
<style>
body {
  font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;
  font-size: 0.8em;
  color:#484848;
}
h1, h2, h3 { font-family: "Trebuchet MS", Verdana, sans-serif; margin: 0px; }
h1 { font-size: 1.2em; }
h2, h3 { font-size: 1.1em; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
Greetings,
<br />
<br />
This message has been automatically generated in response to the
creation of a trouble ticket regarding: "<%= h(@issue.subject) %>",
a summary of which appears below.
<br />
<br />
There is no need to reply to this message right now. Your ticket
has been assigned an ID of <%= "[#{@issue.project.name} - #{@issue.tracker.name} ##{@issue.id}]" %>.
<br />
<br />
Please include the string:
<br />
<br />
<%= "[#{@issue.project.name} - #{@issue.tracker.name} ##{@issue.id}]" %>
<br />
<br />
in the subject line of all future correspondence about this issue.
To do so, you may reply to this message.
<br />
<br />
Please note, we strive to resolve all issues within one business day.
<br />
Thank you for your request,
Support team | <%= link_to @from, @from %>
</body>
</html>
